{
  "stem": "9538.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father and this young boy in the middle of 12, and the other men were brought in and handcuffed and put in front of us, and just shot in front of my mother's and my eyes and the others.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 19, 20-- going on for 20.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Couldn't do anything at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked still in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the conditions were bad, but under those bad conditions, they performed miracles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most complicated operations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were all different recorded aktionen when people were taken away at random.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they would be going, ready to go to their place of work, marching off in their columns to work, the SS would just come in their cars-- they had these open cars-- you know, stopped their cars, jumped out, taken two or three or four or five men out, brought them to the Jewish cemetery for no reason whatsoever, and shot them.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was [? going ?] on all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All the time until-- And then, they made a concentration camp outside Riga, which was called Kaiserwald, where Jewish people worked, and they also had to build the barracks there and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was all what we didn't know in preparation already for the time when the ghetto would be liquidated, which happened on the 2nd of November-- no.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In-- we had German Jewish police for the German Jews, for the [GERMAN] ghetto, they called it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had Latvian Jewish police for the Latvian Jews across the road, which were fantastic young men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were all Zionists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were young students.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were fantastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
